WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.120
Ponyo, stop looking at your phone

2
00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:10.420
Check your phone all day

3
00:00:10.440 --> 00:00:11.820
Oh, Mom.

4
00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:14.040
So late, time to cook

5
00:00:14.040 --> 00:00:15.000
What would you like to eat?

6
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.260
Mom, I can do it.

7
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:18.180
Ok. I'll go for it.

8
00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:31.240
Mom, what's wrong with you?

9
00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:34.780
Mom, don't scare me, mom.

10
00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:46.520
Hello Ponyo Gao Xiangyu

11
00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:49.040
Are you satisfied now, you dog

12
00:00:49.040 --> 00:00:50.160
Mom fed you these days

13
00:00:50.160 --> 00:00:51.280
Now I'm sick again

14
00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:52.400
Come here quickly

15
00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:54.780
I pay my medical bills downstairs in the hospital

16
00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.040
What? Don't worry.

17
00:00:57.040 --> 00:00:58.300
I'll be right there.

18
00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:08.900
How is my sister?

19
00:01:11.080 --> 00:01:12.740
Hey, I've been looking for you everywhere

20
00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:15.380
Doctor, how is my mother's illness?

21
00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:19.120
Yes, the doctor was fine yesterday.

22
00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:22.000
Oh, your mother is so sick that she needs to have surgery quickly.

